    <item>
      <title>印度考虑放宽另类投资基金监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/india-may-ease-rules-for-53-billion-aif-industry-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，在一系列旨在遏制行业错误行为的措施似乎取得成效后，印度市场监管机构可能会放宽对规模 530 亿美元的另类投资基金行业的一些监管规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/india-may-ease-rules-for-53-billion-aif-industry-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 08:06:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济：薪资数据火热，英国央行加重利率谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/uk-economy-hot-wage-data-adds-to-boe-caution-on-rates-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受私营部门薪资大幅上涨的推动，截至 10 月的三个月内，英国常规工资增长速度超过预期，凸显出英国央行对降息的谨慎态度。彭博经济的 Dan Hanson 对数据进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/uk-economy-hot-wage-data-adds-to-boe-caution-on-rates-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 08:01:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管陷入困境的首相留在家中，日本仍与特朗普建立关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/japan-builds-ties-with-trump-even-as-troubled-premier-stays-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管日本不受欢迎的首相留在国内处理不稳定的政治局势，但日本仍在向美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普争取继续保持密切的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/japan-builds-ties-with-trump-even-as-troubled-premier-stays-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:59:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工资上涨后交易员预计英国央行降息幅度将减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示，截至十月份的三个月内，英国工资涨幅超过预期，货币市场大幅解除了对英国央行降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/traders-see-fewer-boe-interest-rate-cuts-after-jump-in-uk-wages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 07:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工资增长一年多来首次回升，抑制降息预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-wage-growth-accelerates-more-than-forecast-to-5-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国常规工资增长一年多来首次加速，促使交易员减少对英国央行降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-wage-growth-accelerates-more-than-forecast-to-5-2</guid>
