    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中国和特朗普影响，亚洲货币指数跌至两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/asian-currency-index-drops-to-two-year-low-as-china-trump-weigh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中国经济前景的悲观情绪以及对特朗普政府将推动美元上涨的猜测，亚洲货币指数跌至两年多以来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/asian-currency-index-drops-to-two-year-low-as-china-trump-weigh</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 05:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治不确定性拖累法国经济增长前景放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/france-s-growth-prospects-weaken-as-political-uncertainty-weighs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任命法国一年内第四位总理几天后，法国央行下调了国内增长预期，央行称政治动荡拖累了家庭和企业信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/france-s-growth-prospects-weaken-as-political-uncertainty-weighs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士钢铁援助即将到来，不再采取放任政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/swiss-steel-aid-draws-closer-in-departure-from-hands-off-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士政府已受议会命令介入，为该国陷入困境的钢铁行业提供援助，此举打破了其传统的不干预商业的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/swiss-steel-aid-draws-closer-in-departure-from-hands-off-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
